This paper deals with wireless communication networks and their optimization, which falls under the Information Theory (cs.IT) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) categories. The paper also involves coordination and control systems, which can be categorized under Systems and Control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of multi-antenna systems, which can be classified under Multimedia (cs.MM) and Computer Engineering (cs.CE) categories.
